- Dad, no! It's not what you think.

885
01:11:11,225 --> 01:11:13,273
- Merida, get back!
- No!

886
01:11:18,357 --> 01:11:20,451
No, Dad! Don't hurt her!

887
01:11:21,360 --> 01:11:23,283
Get out of here!

888
01:11:23,362 --> 01:11:25,956
