- Are you out of your mind, lass?

940
01:17:16,090 --> 01:17:18,263
Mum, are you hurt?

941
01:17:24,807 --> 01:17:25,854
Merida!

942
01:17:27,852 --> 01:17:31,277
I'll not let you kill my mother.

943
01:17:32,231 --> 01:17:33,904
Boys!

944
