959
01:21:21,543 --> 01:21:23,545
I want you back, Mummy.

960
01:21:43,315 --> 01:21:45,317
I love you.

961
01:22:13,053 --> 01:22:15,147
Mum! You're back!

962
01:22:21,937 --> 01:22:23,280
