979
01:23:06,565 --> 01:23:07,987
Show some respect!

980
01:23:12,779 --> 01:23:15,328
Now that's what I call
a wee naked babby!

981
01:23:19,453 --> 01:23:22,172
Merida, Elinor, hurry up.
They're leaving.

982
01:23:22,247 --> 01:23:24,420
- Mum!
- They're off! Come on!

983
01:23:24,500 --> 01:23:26,628
