But how did this...

993
01:24:13,966 --> 01:24:17,470
<i>There are those who say fate
is something beyond our command,</i>

994
01:24:18,303 --> 01:24:20,852
<i>that destiny is not our own.</i>

995
01:24:21,348 --> 01:24:23,350
<i>But I know better.</i>

996
01:24:25,060 --> 01:24:27,563
<i>Our fate lives within us.</i>

997
01:24:29,398 --> 01:24:32,072
<i>You only have to be brave enough
to see it.</i>

998
01:24:39,658 --> 01:24:43,037
<i>We will run and scream</i>

999
01:24:43,120 --> 01:24:46,294
<i>You will dance with me</i>

1000
01:24:46,623 --> 01:24:51,629
<i>We'll fulfill our dreams
and we'll be free</i>

1001
01:24:53,630 --> 01:24:57,055
<i>We will be who we are</i>

