<i>And then heal our scars</i>

1003
01:25:00,637 --> 01:25:05,484
<i>Sadness will be far away</i>

1004
01:25:22,909 --> 01:25:24,877
<i>So I had done wrong</i>

1005
01:25:26,204 --> 01:25:28,582
<i>But you put me right</i>

1006
01:25:29,875 --> 01:25:33,721
<i>My judgment burned
in the black of night</i>

